Description: SalatokApp gtk4 Muslim prayer time manager.
 Get salat timing at your linux desktop
 with full control over the methods adjustment
 this app work with praytimes.org libary under GPL-3.0-or-later thats mean this app can work without connection or sending your personal ip adress to random servers to provide you salat timing
